28,;"Шрифт";profile_editor_section_font,76,V200d73e90,3f00d73ecd,;"Phông chữ";profile_editor_section_font,77,V200d72fce,3800d73004,;"字体";profile_editor_section_font,78,V200d94c0b,5800d94c61,;"字體";profile_editor_section_font,79,V200d72fde,3800d73014,;"字體";file_browser_delete_title,28,V105bf5797,3905bf57cf,;"Delete";terminal_no_route,28,V104a51369,7204a513da,;"Are you trying to access a local host? Grant local network permissions.";terminal_no_route,29,V201dac685,b401dac737,;"Probeer jy om toegang tot ’n plaaslike gasheer te verkry? Verleen toestemming vir die plaaslike netwerk.";terminal_no_route,30,V201cc7fdd,7601cc8051,;"هل تحاول الوصول إلى جهاز محلي؟ امنح التطبيق إذن الوصول إلى الشبكة المحلية.";terminal_no_route,31,V201dacb12,ab01dacbbb,;"Вы спрабуеце падключыцца да хоста ў лакальнай сетцы? Дайце дазвол на доступ да лакальнай сеткі.";terminal_no_route,32,V201daca13,b701dacac8,;"Опитвате ли се да получите достъп до локален хост? Предоставете необходимите разрешения за локалната мрежа.";terminal_no_route,33,V201cc88f7,6c01cc8961,;"Intenteu accedir a un host local? Doneu permís a la xarxa local.";terminal_no_route,34,V201cc8220,7701cc8295,;"Zkoušíte se připojit k místnímu hostiteli? Udělte oprávnění pro místní síť.";terminal_no_route,35,V201dab396,b901dab44d,;"Forsøger du at få adgang til en enhed på det lokale netværk? Giv tilladelse til adgang på det lokale netværk.";terminal_no_route,36,V201cc88e7,8a01cc896f,;"Versuchen Sie auf einen lokalen Host zuzugreifen Grantieren Sie lokale Netzwerk Berechtigungen";terminal_no_route,37,V201dab5b1,af01dab65e,;"Προσπαθείτε να συνδεθείτε σε έναν τοπικό διακομιστή\; Ενεργοποιήστε τις άδειες για το τοπικό δίκτυο.";terminal_no_route,38,V201cc8a0b,7101cc8a7a,;"Estás tratando de acceder a un host local Grant permisos de red local";terminal_no_route,39,V201daabef,a501daac92,;"Sare lokaleko host batera konektatzen saiatzen ari zara? Baimendu sare lokaleko baimenak.";terminal_no_route,40,V201cc851f,7b01cc8598,;"آیا می‌خواهید به یک هاست محلی دسترسی پیدا کنید؟ مجوزهای شبکه محلی را فعال کنید.";terminal_no_route,41,V201dab150,a901dab1f7,;"Yritätkö muodostaa yhteyttä paikalliseen palvelimeen? Anna paikallisen verkon käyttöoikeudet.";terminal_no_route,42,V201cc8aa8,8101cc8b27,;"Essayez-vous d'accéder à un hôte local ? Accordez les autorisations de réseau local.";terminal_no_route,43,V201daac91,9701daad26,;"Está intentando acceder a un host local? Conceda os permisos da rede local.";terminal_no_route,44,V201daa827,9401daa8b9,;"האם אתם מנסים להתחבר למחשב ברשת המקומית? אנא העניקו הרשאות לרשת המקומית.";terminal_no_route,45,V201dac0bc,9d01dac157,;"Pokušavate li pristupiti lokalnom računalu? Odobrite dopuštenja za lokalnu mrežu.";terminal_no_route,46,V201dab7a6,b601dab85a,;"Szeretne hozzáférni egy helyi hálózaton lévő számítógéphez? Engedélyezze a helyi hálózati jogosultságokat.";terminal_no_route,47,V201dab12d,9801dab1c3,;"Apakah Anda mencoba mengakses host lokal? Berikan izin untuk jaringan lokal.";terminal_no_route,48,V201cc8458,7201cc84c8,;"Apakah Anda mencoba mengakses host lokal? Berikan izin jaringan lokal.";terminal_no_route,49,V201dab852,a401dab8f4,;"Ertu að reyna að tengjast tæki á staðarnetinu? Gefðu leyfi fyrir aðgang að staðarnetinu.";terminal_no_route,50,V201cc885a,8501cc88dd,;"Stai cercando di accedere a un host locale? Grantisci le autorizzazioni alla rete locale.";terminal_no_route,51,V201cc7a65,6401cc7ac7,;"האם אתה מנסה לגשת למחשב מקומי? הענק הרשאות לרשת המקומית.";terminal_no_route,52,V201cc6e86,5e01cc6ee2,;"ローカルホストにアクセスしようとしていますか ローカルネットワークのパーミッションを付与してください";terminal_no_route,53,V201dabdad,a801dabe53,;"სურავთ\, ადგილობრივ სერვერთან დაკავშირება? მოგვცეთ უფლება ადგილობრივი ქსელის გამოყენებისთვის.";terminal_no_route,54,V201cc6d62,5401cc6db4,;"로컬 호스트에 액세스하려고 하십니까? 로컬 네트워크 권한을 부여하십시오.";terminal_no_route,55,V201daa4d5,ae01daa581,;"ທ່ານກໍາລັງພະຍາຍາມເຂົ້າເຖິງເຄື່ອງແມ່ຂ່າຍໃນເຄືອນຂ່າຍທ້ອງຖິ່ນບໍ? ກະລຸນາອະນຸຍາດສິດໃນເຄືອນຂ່າຍທ້ອງຖິ່ນ.";terminal_no_route,56,V201dacc7b,aa01dacd23,;"Ar bandote prisijungti prie vietinio tinklo kompiuterio? Suteikite leidimus vietiniam tinklui.";terminal_no_route,57,V201dac02a,9901dac0c1,;"Vai mēģināt piekļūt lokālajam serverim? Piešķiriet atļaujas lokālajam tīklam.";terminal_no_route,58,V201dac341,b001dac3ef,;"Дали се обидувате да пристапите до локален хост? Дозволете ги потребните дозволи за локалната мрежа.";terminal_no_route,59,V201dab037,be01dab0f3,;"Prøver du å få tilgang til en enhet på det lokale nettverket? Gi tillatelse for tilgang til det lokale nettverket.";terminal_no_route,60,V201dacad5,bf01dacb92,;"के तपाईं स्थानीय नेटवर्कमा रहेको कुनै उपकरणमा पहुँच गर्न खोज्दै हुनुहुन्छ? कृपया स्थानीय नेटवर्कको अनुमति दिनुहोस्।";terminal_no_route,61,V201cc890e,9801cc89a4,;"Probeer je toegang te krijgen tot een lokale host? Geef dan toestemming voor toegang tot het lokale netwerk.";terminal_no_route,62,V201cc85e4,7d01cc865f,;"Czy próbujesz uzyskać dostęp do lokalnego hosta? Użyj uprawnienia sieci lokalnej.";terminal_no_route,63,V201cc874a,7601cc87be,;"Você está tentando acessar um host local? Conceda permissões à rede local.";terminal_no_route,64,V201cc85da,7501cc864d,;"Você está tentando acessar um host local? Grant permissões de rede local.";terminal_no_route,65,V201dac83a,b301dac8eb,;"Încercați să accesați un host din rețeaua locală? Acordați permisiunile necesare pentru rețeaua locală.";terminal_no_route,66,V201cc8561,8c01cc85eb,;"Вы пытаетесь получить доступ к локальному хосту? Выберите разрешение на доступ к локальной сети.";terminal_no_route,67,V201dab479,a301dab51a,;"Pokúšate sa pripojiť k lokálnemu hostiteľovi? Povolenie pre lokálnu sieť musíte udeliť.";terminal_no_route,68,V201dab2aa,9b01dab343,;"Poskušate se povezati z lokalnim gostiteljem? Dovolite dostop do lokalne mreže.";terminal_no_route,69,V201daafb7,ab01dab060,;"Да ли покушавате да се повежете са уређајем у локалној мрежи? Дозволите приступ локалној мрежи.";terminal_no_route,70,V201dab3cc,bf01dab489,;"Försöker du ansluta till en enhet i det lokala nätverket? Ge programmet tillstånd att använda det lokala nätverket.";terminal_no_route,71,V201dad09a,b701dad14f,;"உள்ளூர் நெட்வொர்க்கில் உள்ள ஒரு சேவையகத்தை அணுக முயற்சிக்கிறீர்களா? உள்ளூர் நெட்வொர்க் அனுமதிகளை வழங்கவும்.";terminal_no_route,72,V201dac2ee,b201dac39e,;"คุณกำลังพยายามเข้าถึงเครื่องในเครือข่ายท้องถิ่นใช่หรือไม่ โปรดอนุญาตสิทธิ์การเข้าถึงเครือข่ายท้องถิ่น.";terminal_no_route,73,V201dac9b9,9b01daca52,;"Siz ýerli serwere ýa-da ulgama ýetmek isleýäňizmi? Ýerli ulgam üçin rugsat ber.";terminal_no_route,74,V201dab271,9501dab304,;"Yerel bir sunucuya erişmeye mi çalışıyorsunuz? Yerel ağ izinlerini verin.";terminal_no_route,75,V201cc89b9,8501cc8a3c,;"Ви намагаєтеся отримати доступ до локального хоста? Надайте дозволи для локальної мережі.";terminal_no_route,76,V201cc8469,8201cc84e9,;"Bạn có đang cố gắng truy cập máy chủ cục bộ không? Hãy cấp quyền truy cập mạng cục bộ.";terminal_no_route,77,V201cc66bf,4401cc6701,;"您是否正在尝试访问本地主机？请授予本地网络权限。";terminal_no_route,78,V201daa703,6901daa76a,;"您是否正在嘗試連接至本機網路上的主機？請授予本機網路權限。";terminal_no_route,79,V201cc6761,4401cc67a3,;"您是否正在嘗試存取本機主機？請授予本機網路權限。";prompt_bits,28,V100a129de,2c00a12a09,;"Bits\:";prompt_bits,29,V20043185f,4b004318a8,;"Bite\:";prompt_bits,30,V200431207,2d00431232,;"البتات\:";prompt_bits,31,V200431b49,4b00431b92,;"Біты\:";prompt_bits,32,V20017057b,2c001705a5,;"Битове";prompt_bits,33,V2004312e2,2a0043130a,;"Bits";prompt_bits,34,V200431240,310043126f,;"Počet bitů\:";prompt_bits,35,V2001e07c4,2a001e07ec,;"Bit\:";prompt_bits,36,V200431380,2b004313a9,;"Bits\:";prompt_bits,37,V200290b41,2b00290b6a,;"Bits\:";prompt_bits,38,V200431341,2b0043136a,;"Bits\:";prompt_bits,39,V200290a43,2c00290a6d,;"Bitak\:";prompt_bits,40,V2004312d0,2d004312fb,;"بیت ها\:";prompt_bits,41,V2002208c5,2e002208f1,;"Bittejä\:";prompt_bits,42,V200431370,2c0043139a,;"Bits \:";prompt_bits,43,V200290a4f,2b00290a78,;"Bits\:";prompt_bits,44,V2001f0771,2d001f079c,;"סיביות\:";prompt_bits,45,V2001e078e,2b001e07b7,;"Bits\:";prompt_bits,46,V2001e07bc,2c001e07e6,;"Bitek\:";prompt_