,;"Ctrl\+A potom mezeru";list_camera_ctrlaspace_description,35,V20221d38a,840221d40c,;"Ctrl\+A\, efterfulgt af mellemrumstasten.";list_camera_ctrlaspace_description,36,V20213a065,520213a0b5,;"Strg\+A dann Leertaste";list_camera_ctrlaspace_description,37,V20221d873,840221d8f5,;"Ctrl\+A και μετά το πλήκτρο διαστήματος.";list_camera_ctrlaspace_description,38,V20213a125,510213a174,;"Ctrl\+A luego Espacio";list_camera_ctrlaspace_description,39,V20221cc4e,780221ccc4,;"Ctrl\+A\, gero Espazio-barra.";list_camera_ctrlaspace_description,40,V202139ba6,5402139bf8,;"Ctrl\+A و سپس کلید Space";list_camera_ctrlaspace_description,41,V20221d177,840221d1f9,;"Ctrl\+A\, jonka jälkeen välilyöntinäppäin";list_camera_ctrlaspace_description,42,V20213a223,4f0213a270,;"Ctrl\+A puis Espace";list_camera_ctrlaspace_description,43,V20221cd15,7a0221cd8d,;"Ctrl\+A e logo a tecla Espacio";list_camera_ctrlaspace_description,44,V20221c650,720221c6c0,;"Ctrl\+A\, ואז מקש הרווח";list_camera_ctrlaspace_description,45,V20221e12b,770221e1a0,;"Ctrl\+A\, zatim tipka Space.";list_camera_ctrlaspace_description,46,V20221d883,7c0221d8fd,;"Ctrl\+A\, majd a szóköz billentyű";list_camera_ctrlaspace_description,47,V20221d0ff,7b0221d178,;"Ctrl\+A lalu tekan tombol Spasi";list_camera_ctrlaspace_description,48,V202139ae5,4e02139b31,;"Ctrl\+A lalu Spasi";list_camera_ctrlaspace_description,49,V20221d8b9,8d0221d944,;"Haltu niður Ctrl\+A og ýttu síðan á bilastangina.";list_camera_ctrlaspace_description,50,V202139f2f,4e02139f7b,;"Ctrl\+A poi spazio";list_camera_ctrlaspace_description,51,V202138f41,4c02138f8b,;"Ctrl\+A ואז רווח";list_camera_ctrlaspace_description,52,V202138098,48021380de,;"CtrlAの後スペース";list_camera_ctrlaspace_description,53,V20221deba,7f0221df37,;"Ctrl\+A\, შემდეგ – კოსმოსური ღილაკი.";list_camera_ctrlaspace_description,54,V202137f72,5602137fc6,;"CtrlA，然后空格을 누르면 CtrlA스페이스";list_camera_ctrlaspace_description,55,V20221c4eb,800221c569,;"ກົດ Ctrl\+A ຫຼັງຈາກນັ້ນກົດປຸ່ມ Space";list_camera_ctrlaspace_description,56,V20221ecfc,8c0221ed86,;"Paspauskite „Ctrl\+A“\, o paskui – tarpo klavišą.";list_camera_ctrlaspace_description,57,V20221e0df,750221e152,;"Ctrl\+A\, pēc tam atstarpe";list_camera_ctrlaspace_description,58,V20221e40f,740221e481,;"Ctrl\+A\, потоа интервал.";list_camera_ctrlaspace_description,59,V20221cfbf,7e0221d03b,;"Ctrl\+A\, deretter mellomromstasten";list_camera_ctrlaspace_description,60,V20221eb8a,860221ec0e,;"Ctrl\+A\, त्यसपछि स्पेस (Space) थिच्नुहोस्।";list_camera_ctrlaspace_description,61,V20213a057,5e0213a0b3,;"Ctrl\+A gevolgd door de spatiebalk";list_camera_ctrlaspace_description,62,V202139dfa,5402139e4c,;"Ctrl\+A następnie Spacja";list_camera_ctrlaspace_description,63,V202139e4a,5502139e9d,;"Ctrl\+A seguido de Espaço";list_camera_ctrlaspace_description,64,V202139cb2,5002139d00,;"Ctrl\+A então Espaço";list_camera_ctrlaspace_description,65,V20221e944,770221e9b9,;"Ctrl\+A\, apoi tasta Spațiu.";list_camera_ctrlaspace_description,66,V202139c94,5002139ce2,;"Ctrl\+A затем пробел";list_camera_ctrlaspace_description,67,V20221d49c,780221d512,;"Ctrl\+A\, potom kláves Space.";list_camera_ctrlaspace_description,68,V20221d3bf,790221d436,;"Ctrl\+A\, nato pa preslednica.";list_camera_ctrlaspace_description,69,V20221cfde,7e0221d05a,;"Ctrl\+A\, zatim taster sa razmakom.";list_camera_ctrlaspace_description,70,V20221d3b5,810221d434,;"Ctrl\+A följt av mellanslagstangenten";list_camera_ctrlaspace_description,71,V20221f2ba,8e0221f346,;"Ctrl\+A\, பின்னர் இடைவெளி (Space) பட்டனை அழுத்தவும்";list_camera_ctrlaspace_description,72,V20221e272,7c0221e2ec,;"กด Ctrl\+A แล้วตามด้วยปุ่ม Space";list_camera_ctrlaspace_description,73,V20221ea15,790221ea8c,;"Ctrl\+A\, soňra boşluk düwmesi";list_camera_ctrlaspace_description,74,V20221d2af,790221d326,;"Ctrl\+A\, ardından Boşluk tuşu";list_camera_ctrlaspace_description,75,V20213a0b4,510213a103,;"Ctrl\+A\, потім пробіл";list_camera_ctrlaspace_description,76,V202139bc2,5f02139c1f,;"Nhấn Ctrl\+A\, sau đó nhấn phím cách";list_camera_ctrlaspace_description,