in,74,V2002609cb,2f002609f8,;"(tekrar)";prompt_again,75,V200401233,2e0040125f,;"(знову)";prompt_again,76,V20040116f,310040119e,;"(nhập lại)";prompt_again,77,V200400dd8,2d00400e03,;"(再次输入)";prompt_again,78,V2004015c0,4d0040160b,;"（再次輸入）";prompt_again,79,V200400de8,3000400e16,;"(再輸入一次密碼)";network_restored_ip_changed,28,V100d338fb,6500d3395f,;"Network restored but IP changed\, reconnecting…";network_restored_ip_changed,29,V2005722a5,9200572335,;"Netwerk herstel\, maar IP-adres verander\, herstel verbinding…";network_restored_ip_changed,30,V2005718d6,7000571944,;"تم استعادة الشبكة ولكن تم تغيير عنوان IP، إعادة الاتصال...";network_restored_ip_changed,31,V200572501,a3005725a2,;"Злучэнне з сеткай адноўлена\, але IP-адрас зменены\, ідзе паўновае падключэнне…";network_restored_ip_changed,32,V2005c2323,a7005c23c8,;"Мрежата е възстановена\, но IP адресът е променен\, извършва се повторно свързване…";network_restored_ip_changed,33,V200571a89,8500571b0c,;"La xarxa s'ha restablert\, però l'adreça IP ha canviat\, tornant a connectar...";network_restored_ip_changed,34,V200571910,7400571982,;"Síť byla obnovena ale IP adresa se změnila připojuji se znovu…";network_restored_ip_changed,35,V200bf3c9a,a400bf3d3c,;"Netværket er genoprettet\, men IP-adressen er ændret. Genopretter forbindelse …";network_restored_ip_changed,36,V200571b30,7000571b9e,;"Netzwerk wiederhergestellt aber IP geändert neu verbinden…";network_restored_ip_changed,37,V200fc51e8,ab00fc5291,;"Το δίκτυο έχει αποκατασταθεί\, αλλά η διεύθυνση IP έχει αλλάξει\, γίνεται επανασύνδεση…";network_restored_ip_changed,38,V200571ad3,7100571b42,;"Red de restaurada pero la dirección IP cambio reconectando…";network_restored_ip_changed,39,V200fc4d6d,9600fc4e01,;"Sarea berreskuratu da\, baina IP-a aldatu da\, berriz konektatzen…";network_restored_ip_changed,40,V2005719ec,7500571a5f,;"شبکه دوباره فعال شد اما آدرس IP تغییر کرد، در حال اتصال مجدد...";network_restored_ip_changed,41,V200dd4392,ab00dd443b,;"Verkkoyhteys palautettu\, mutta IP